# notes:
# - backend/migrations is tracked source code and should stay versioned.
# - backend/middleware/memiserve.json stays ignored because it is a local credential file.
# - backend/uploads stays ignored because uploaded assets are deployment/runtime files.
# - backups/ is intentionally not ignored so handover database exports can be committed.

npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
